sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Cluster Operator
    participant CLI as rhai-cli Binary
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant FS as Local Filesystem

    Note over User,FS: Flow 1: Upgrade Lint Assessment (rhai-cli lint --target-version X.Y)

    User->>CLI: rhai-cli lint --target-version 3.5
    CLI->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Access granted/denied
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET DSCInitialization, DataScienceCluster<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Platform configuration
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET OLM Subscriptions, CSVs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Operator versions & dependencies
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET InferenceServices, Notebooks, DSPAs,<br/>RayClusters, ClusterQueues, etc.<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Workload resources
    Note over CLI: Execute 38+ version-aware checks<br/>(dependencies, services, platform,<br/>components, workloads)
    CLI-->>User: Structured lint results<br/>(critical/warning/info + remediation)

    Note over User,FS: Flow 2: Migration Prepare + Run (rhai-cli migrate prepare/run)

    User->>CLI: rhai-cli migrate prepare --target-version 3.5
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET target resources<br/>(ISVCs, SRs, Notebooks, DSPAs, etc.)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Resources to migrate
    CLI->>FS: Write backup YAML files
    FS-->>CLI: Backup confirmed
    CLI->>K8sAPI: Validate prerequisites<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Prerequisites met
    CLI-->>User: Prepare results (backups created)

    User->>CLI: rhai-cli migrate run --target-version 3.5
    Note over CLI: Execute migration actions sequentially<br/>(stream progress via StepRecorder)
    CLI->>K8sAPI: PATCH InferenceServices<br/>(deploymentMode → RawDeployment)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Patched
    CLI->>K8sAPI: PATCH ServingRuntimes<br/>(multi-model → single-model)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Patched
    CLI->>K8sAPI: PATCH Notebooks<br/>(container name fix)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Patched
    CLI->>K8sAPI: CREATE/DELETE RayClusters<br/>(backup, delete, recreate)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Migrated
    CLI-->>User: Migration results<br/>(success/failure per action)

    Note over User,FS: Flow 3: TrustyAI Metrics Backup/Restore

    User->>CLI: rhai-cli migrate prepare --action trustyai.metrics
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET TrustyAIServices,<br/>Discover OpenShift Routes<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: TrustyAI endpoints
    CLI->>TrustyAI: GET /metrics (backup)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (via Route)
    TrustyAI-->>CLI: Metrics JSON
    CLI->>FS: Write metrics backup JSON
    FS-->>CLI: Saved

    User->>CLI: rhai-cli migrate run --action trustyai.metrics
    CLI->>FS: Read metrics backup JSON
    FS-->>CLI: Metrics data
    CLI->>TrustyAI: POST /metrics (restore)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (via Route)
    TrustyAI-->>CLI: Restore confirmed
    CLI-->>User: Metrics restored successfully
